                    {
                        "name": "Divine Spontaneous Spells",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "DC 28, attack +20; <b>4th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"6\" game-obj=\"Spells\">air walk</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"146\" game-obj=\"Spells\">harm</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"247\" game-obj=\"Spells\">read omens</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"329\" game-obj=\"Spells\">talking corpse</a></u></i> (3 slots); <b>3rd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"22\" game-obj=\"Spells\">bind undead</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"26\" game-obj=\"Spells\">blindness</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"36\" game-obj=\"Spells\">chilling darkness</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"354\" game-obj=\"Spells\">vampiric touch</a></u></i> (4 slots); <b>2nd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"59\" game-obj=\"Spells\">darkness</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"63\" game-obj=\"Spells\">death knell</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"256\" game-obj=\"Spells\">resist energy</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"271\" game-obj=\"Spells\">see invisibility</a></u></i> (4 slots); <b>1st</b><i><u><a aonid=\"18\" game-obj=\"Spells\">bane</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"45\" game-obj=\"Spells\">command</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"110\" game-obj=\"Spells\">fear</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"356\" game-obj=\"Spells\">ventriloquism</a></u></i> (4 slots); <b>Cantrips</b><b>(4th)</b><i><u><a aonid=\"35\" game-obj=\"Spells\">chill touch</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"66\" game-obj=\"Spells\">detect magic</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"142\" game-obj=\"Spells\">guidance</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"171\" game-obj=\"Spells\">light</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"246\" game-obj=\"Spells\">read aura</a></u></i><br/><b>Occult Innate Spells</b> DC 28; <b>6th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"87\" game-obj=\"Spells\">dominate</a></u></i>; <b>5th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"161\" game-obj=\"Spells\">illusory scene</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"315\" game-obj=\"Spells\">suggestion</a></u></i>; <b>3rd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"159\" game-obj=\"Spells\">illusory disguise</a></u></i> (at will); <b>2nd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"197\" game-obj=\"Spells\">mirror image</a></u></i> (at will); <b>1st</b><i><u><a aonid=\"356\" game-obj=\"Spells\">ventriloquism</a></u></i> (at will)<br/><b>Rituals</b> DC 28; <b>2nd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Rituals\">create undead</a></u></i><br/>",
                        "subtype": "spells"
