                    {
                        "name": "Raise Serpent",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "<b>Frequency</b> once per day; <b>Effect</b> The bone prophet animates corpses of snakes, serpentfolk, or similar serpentine creatures within a 30-foot emanation. Any flesh on the bodies sloughs off, and they rise as skeletons. The bone prophet can raise one Large creature as a <a aonid=\"375\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">skeletal giant</a> or up to three Medium creatures as <a aonid=\"373\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">skeletal champions</a>; the equipment and attacks might be different depending on the corpses' possessionsThese skeletons have the <a aonid=\"109\" game-obj=\"Traits\">minion</a> trait and are under the bone prophet's control; the bone prophet can give all these minions the same command with a single action that has the <a aonid=\"32\" game-obj=\"Traits\">concentrate</a> trait. Any skeletal minions that still remain after 10 minutes crumble to dust.",
                        "action": {
                            "type": "stat_block_section",
